it's gonna be tough to fight if you can't hear!

323
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:25,620
Check it out!

324
00:22:25,410 --> 00:22:29,700
Scratchmen Apoo
(Captain of the On Air Pirates)
Informant to the Beast Pirates
Bounty: 350 Million Berries

325
00:22:58,610 --> 00:23:00,110
Jaki!

326
00:23:04,450 --> 00:23:05,950
Goki!

327
00:23:09,950 --> 00:23:11,700
Juki!

328
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:17,080
It's too painful to see you guys like this!

329
00:23:17,080 --> 00:23:21,170
Th-The ten of you...

330
00:23:21,630 --> 00:23:26,510
have leveled countless towns together!

331
00:23:29,390 --> 00:23:31,850
That's why...

332
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:37,940
it's just not fair to get
your asses kicked while drunk...

333
00:23:37,940 --> 00:23:40,360
at such a delightful banquet!

334
00:23:50,950 --> 00:23:51,660
Right?!

335
00:23:51,660 --> 00:23:55,750
Don't you think so... Haccha?!

336
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:03,090
Are you sobered up now?!

337
00:24:06,470 --> 00:24:08,760
There are ten of them?!

338
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:10,930
I'm gonna need more cola!

339
00:24:10,930 --> 00:24:13,560
There's always strength in numbers!

340
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:17,810
Time to teach these lousy fools...

341
00:24:17,810 --> 00:24:22,400
what happens when
an ancient giant loses their cool!

342
00:24:24,730 --> 00:24:27,400
What?! Is he their tamer or something?

343
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:29,030
That jerk!

344
00:24:29,030 --> 00:24:30,030
Forget about it!

345
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:31,410
We gotta go!

346
00:24:32,120 --> 00:24:33,410
Fine!

347
00:24:33,410 --> 00:24:34,290
Let's go!

348
00:24:34,290 --> 00:24:35,160
Yeah!

349
00:24:39,420 --> 00:24:43,040
It's just about showtime!

350
00:24:43,040 --> 00:24:44,800
No room for you guys on stage!

351
00:24:44,800 --> 00:24:46,460
This is a solo performance!

352
00:24:47,630 --> 00:24:49,050
Don't stop, Luffy!

353
00:24:49,050 --> 00:24:50,550
Yeah, I got it!

354
00:25:17,580 --> 00:25:19,120
Look how strong he is!

355
00:25:19,460 --> 00:25:22,290
Don't tell me he's going
to use his ally as a weapon!

356
00:25:23,330 --> 00:25:24,460
Oh no!

357
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:38,350
Franky! Run straight out of the dome!

358
00:25:39,770 --> 00:25:44,690
If we let this monstrosity run amok
any longer, the samurai will be overwhelmed!

359
00:25:44,690 --> 00:25:46,400
Sure thing!

360
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:47,480
I'm counting on you!

361
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:48,360
Yeah!

362
00:25:53,570 --> 00:25:58,200
Does he think the General Franky
is some kind of action figure?!

363
00:26:00,580 --> 00:26:04,250
You're not getting your grubby hands on me!

364
00:26:06,210 --> 00:26:09,800
He's gonna regret...

365
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:13,130
treating it like a toy!

366
00:26:14,510 --> 00:26:15,720
At the very least...

367
00:26:17,930 --> 00:26:21,890
it's a much better outcome
for me if you guys win.

368
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,940
Is that convincing enough?!

369
00:26:31,860 --> 00:26:32,900
I see.

370
00:26:32,900 --> 00:26:35,450
You're pretty straightforward.

371
00:26:35,450 --> 00:26:36,320
But...

372
00:26:40,120 --> 00:26:43,580
you're still hiding your identity!

373
00:26:43,580 --> 00:26:46,670
We can't fight with a guy like that!

374
00:26:53,050 --> 00:26:55,590
I just got a good idea!

375
00:26:55,590 --> 00:26:57,970
Let's call in a few more Numbers!

376
00:26:58,560 --> 00:27:01,180
Hey, guys!

377
00:27:01,180 --> 00:27:04,600
Sober up and get over here!

378
00:27:08,230 --> 00:27:10,480
Knock that shit off!

379
00:27:14,700 --> 00:27:17,660
Yo, yo! I heard about you, Drake!

380
00:27:18,870 --> 00:27:23,330
Are you gonna leech off that
itty-bitty pirate crew now?!

381
00:27:25,330 --> 00:27:27,500
Scratchmen Apoo!

382
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:30,170
I've always hated this guy!

383
00:27:30,500 --> 00:27:33,420
I'll kick his ass, but I'm not
doing it for you guys!

384
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:36,340
What's this? Common ground?

385
00:27:37,140 --> 00:27:40,010
I don't like him either.

386
00:27:42,350 --> 00:27:45,600
Looks like... we've got an alliance!

387
00:27:46,020 --> 00:27:47,480
What the heck?!

388
00:28:06,580 --> 00:28:09,500
Drake!

389
00:28:14,510 --> 00:28:19,260
Don't think you can get away, you traitor!

390
00:28:19,260 --> 00:28:23,720
I mean, you gotta be a spy!

391
00:28:24,640 --> 00:28:28,020
You've got another freak coming after you...

392
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:32,070
Did you think that crap
would be enough to take me down?

393
00:28:32,070 --> 00:28:33,780
Ow, ow, ow...

394
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:35,900
Hey, stay with me!

395
00:28:36,900 --> 00:28:38,820
Ouch! Dammit!

396
00:28:38,820 --> 00:28:40,370
You're okay!

397
00:28:40,370 --> 00:28:41,740
It's a shallow wound!

398
00:29:08,020 --> 00:29:09,060
Is this...?!

399
00:29:11,520 --> 00:29:12,650
Don't tell me...

400
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:14,900
this bullet...

401
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:39,300
Now... scamper around,
exhaust your strength, then die!

402
00:29:41,930 --> 00:29:46,680
I can't wait to see how many you can dodge!

403
00:29:51,310 --> 00:29:53,560
The thought never crossed my mind.

404
00:29:54,110 --> 00:29:56,820
Blast Breath!

405
00:29:58,320 --> 00:29:59,990
Foxfire Style...

406
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:06,080
Flame-Rend!

407
00:30:34,600 --> 00:30:36,230
You thought we would flee?

408
00:30:36,900 --> 00:30:38,780
How amusing!

409
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:41,690
We are done running!

410
00:30:42,110 --> 00:30:44,450
And done hiding!

411
00:30:44,450 --> 00:30:49,540
Let us die as Lord Oden's samurai!

412
00:30:51,660 --> 00:30:54,500
Firmly grasping your severed head!
